text: Ma Janine Hansen (born 5 July 1989), known as Janine Hansen, is a Luxembourger former footballer who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Luxembourg women's national team. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers Category:Luxembourgian people of Filipino descent
